{"id":"33546309e42b7009ef0eba0f027cfe32ffad09c0666e623db566eac91c0c72c4","item_id":"86273c707e:0","text":"Tractor 会将任务分发到由执行服务器组成的 render farm（渲染农场）。它会管理来自多个用户的大量并发 job queue（作业队列），同时执行依赖关系和调度策略。"}
{"id":"be395e4777a5b8f9da43374cf2ccdbec0c80a171abfe12bdd3128860f7b0d591","item_id":"86273c707e:1","text":"在 Solaris 中，点击任意 UI pane（UI 面板）中的 + 图标即可打开 Tractor Spool panel（Tractor 提交面板）。"}
{"id":"e9180c0567de06b4169031913db638a4b7431bc542c9ce5d9272fc775c89ce94","item_id":"86273c707e:2","text":"Spool to（提交到）"}
{"id":"984cfe27b73d034410351f34b421cb1c326eb5d957a330a7954fdb224863fe9b","item_id":"86273c707e:3","text":"选择将作业提交到 LocalQueue 还是 Tractor farm"}
{"id":"eb463ce8f83db65d128198893fd97663f8bc7e65e8beca642c2db8112efe1b45","item_id":"86273c707e:4","text":"Render Node（渲染节点）"}
{"id":"a8f1863e201e29f26c8f2921f3127282999b4f01ac83d599362a62856769bb60","item_id":"86273c707e:5","text":"选择要提交的 USD Render ROP 节点"}
{"id":"1a4ebec9c1477af65c1427ddf9f6ab60433fb1a922c9000412b2b6e6f52c3166","item_id":"86273c707e:6","text":"Render Threads（渲染线程）"}
{"id":"8b2cc703ffe26cb53a8c1de0f842152dde02c819b06e0a3857093af8bb7c738f","item_id":"86273c707e:7","text":"用于渲染的线程数。0 表示使用所有可用线程。"}
{"id":"b6416e2ac7740df2b1ed8c610d7a9cfa48740008c5fe557cb51843fca628556d","item_id":"86273c707e:8","text":"Engine Host（Engine 主机）"}
{"id":"dfa9f1c846fe24265f95fece1d8c2ba92d232c275dbf8cb35f0b18b4c5008bfe","item_id":"86273c707e:9","text":"运行 Tractor Engine 的机器主机名。"}
{"id":"220504fec427daa0be05e52626256bf63c29486fe35b82a3a69d03a9e02e1af3","item_id":"86273c707e:10","text":"Engine Port（Engine 端口）"}
{"id":"11e923adcf978ee8a646c72f04790bef3d80cfd8dbadc74385cd20f9f4f50c5d","item_id":"86273c707e:11","text":"Tractor Engine 监听的端口。默认值为 80"}
{"id":"b512d97e7cbf97c273e4db073bbb547aa65a84589227f8f3d9e4a72b9372a24d","item_id":"86273c707e:12","text":"User（用户）"}
{"id":"e4d8956b440c6188ed831dc0f02f6b5298725a36c68430d6a244ff607bab6bb7","item_id":"86273c707e:13","text":"提交作业的用户名。"}
{"id":"e159b06187d369a0615f66ce577582b5c983d4ea59b3a62b702049f61753f0bf","item_id":"86273c707e:14","text":"Paused（暂停）"}
{"id":"01df9fb809f7e09ef318d48665fdaad34f33000e23853287d823c3da69c1eb51","item_id":"86273c707e:15","text":"选中此选项时，作业会以 paused（暂停）状态提交。"}
{"id":"447d9363f7225cf710a5bbc4e1a4200b14ca968bee921b086dfe00b3d13fa1a8","item_id":"86273c707e:16","text":"Delete Temp Files（删除临时文件）"}
{"id":"ec1b9a525ddcabd2d4d1f930d30a291a3e0da3b584e84a7a42306091e712f57a","item_id":"86273c707e:17","text":"删除批量渲染所需的所有临时文件"}
{"id":"d60dbba079223254d4c49c230a515bc107a997e69f811365da2387f8557b9cec","item_id":"86273c707e:18","text":"Priority（优先级）"}
{"id":"391c40df5dcf044ca929a4359041dac778d7537c280e7fd677970bd2a9367361","item_id":"86273c707e:19","text":"作业的优先级。"}
{"id":"d677190e0a9990e7d5fa9e4c1bbde44271fb8959c4acb6d43e02ed991128b4bf","item_id":"86273c707e:20","text":"Service（服务）"}
{"id":"0b40b060550964456573fa9bb9dbf6d776eb35096f32b6c1db93e6fd7be22027","item_id":"86273c707e:21","text":"此作业的 Service keys（服务键）。"}
{"id":"0a4679ac1177b0e9bdd1cd17fdf93eb6ef15bb8ecbd7d1d63f342c74946d216d","item_id":"86273c707e:22","text":"Env Keys（环境键）"}
{"id":"e9b0a815759213b8042fb45e115bfa2d73441ca0f59e8404ce1ca86eec66b33f","item_id":"86273c707e:23","text":"可以指定多个 key，之间应以空格分隔。"}
{"id":"4303bc09b0f601bc006f05765c5e2de767362ed13f9174dc78b82e666394c062","item_id":"86273c707e:24","text":"LocalQueue 和 Tractor 开箱即可识别以下 environment keys（环境键）："}
{"id":"0c36332ad8d2cfeb5964dab3a2eb5534078e6ef0e91f3685cf0b7cab0106a2fc","item_id":"86273c707e:25","text":"- prman-*（例如 prman-24.0）"}
{"id":"1e7e2b445c797b264509d389c92ad65b33c8f217e02b5bd1296a1253dfd5b348","item_id":"86273c707e:26","text":"- rmantree=*（例如 rmantree=$RMANTREE）"}
{"id":"7b68fe5510851da3d89100c569d3265e044d8656d95750c376b7a0972dea7330","item_id":"86273c707e:27","text":"After（之后）"}
{"id":"d0d7729ba70c6b11cd75e41545e9bf71e1b47bd7fe89dfbd923dd4200008edd9","item_id":"86273c707e:28","text":"将作业处理的开始时间延迟到指定时间"}
{"id":"544ba0516fd8e5c06858b28f1f71b0630a52f5ef2e69b9eb26ac7cfaa80dfc8b","item_id":"86273c707e:29","text":"格式：MONTH/DAY HOUR:MINUTES"}
{"id":"7a88fbd78bcf9a12f5fb9cda8a951ee635d0bb36055a718dc8db92582a2a1177","item_id":"86273c707e:30","text":"例如：11/24 13:45"}
{"id":"c1f4e23e514e1afba0ed7746b72053757d252f5ae10bb788c476aa42ad25149a","item_id":"86273c707e:31","text":"Crews（团队）"}
{"id":"438571dc2bb415d8be4ef91a8712357e23a9521301a5847ad7230d337e685763","item_id":"86273c707e:32","text":"Crews 列表。"}
{"id":"1eae7b58e784ce762caa0c5888578002c76009df402d9da5643d6954baa4bc4d","item_id":"86273c707e:33","text":"请参见 Tractor 文档中的 'Crews'。"}
{"id":"cb9e8664edea8cf5965fb4d4d013974ef10caeaad734702b19617210828cd7ab","item_id":"86273c707e:34","text":"Tier（层级）"}
{"id":"d899356e0a8cf86366bff2bcdff9cb245e8bd2423889a1d54826a4a38df9e512","item_id":"86273c707e:35","text":"该作业所属的 dispatching tier（调度层级）。"}
{"id":"d24abb4a3f06cc6c73ac5117314c5b7a89925c9e68dc6edc6add0b126335a195","item_id":"86273c707e:36","text":"请参见 Tractor 文档中的 Scheduling Modes。"}
{"id":"04e2a9728af7584043c5d58ae29e7cd811883e8dab15fc6287675270669a3ada","item_id":"86273c707e:37","text":"Projects（项目）"}
{"id":"69032d91e738d976c4e21a9034a362e01b3a83fb96f8ced97fc0d6f550c5b992","item_id":"86273c707e:38","text":"该作业所属的项目。"}
{"id":"048c97c5d0c0bfd0511b3e71bcde98ee7e7a4f2911166d1d4ee7c565d42a1e79","item_id":"86273c707e:39","text":"请参见 Tractor 文档中的 'Limits Configuration'"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"86273c707e:40","text":"。"}
{"id":"355f79f29d7d3c2df917ad07f7441e3ce4b0ac48892b778076dbdca401851712","item_id":"86273c707e:41","text":"Comments（注释）"}
{"id":"28428af7f2767919954fa75523b1aee3ab3617b3b848a24d0ab3cb44285b1947","item_id":"86273c707e:42","text":"关于该作业的附加注释"}
{"id":"9eddf573cb509f1f62df633e25c052ac1b2a0ff9241e70223c77c73e834c0045","item_id":"86273c707e:43","text":"Metadata（元数据）"}
{"id":"61a738c61ecbbbb2c0bca3aef70cb115c5fe16e79c2fcf5efb3e3e18c7d4f8cb","item_id":"86273c707e:44","text":"要添加到作业上的 metadata（元数据）。"}
{"id":"50886b93ae7338bcec5e0d16a15130df9aa0592d62aee3d3c02b3e4fbbd2e8a6","item_id":"86273c707e:45","text":"When Done Command（成功完成时命令）"}
{"id":"a2d3c93645f79b02bc84369ae2c6209b7522487019275f9c40b92cec93c7789c","item_id":"86273c707e:46","text":"作业无错误完成时运行的命令。"}
{"id":"b614de6909b79e4e093a52c93f0f8b8b2637b01d27cdcd879af5711cd49e078f","item_id":"86273c707e:47","text":"When Always Command（始终运行命令）"}
{"id":"28f9fb6e847dc004aeea3eaaa42f9cb193b6c01082d2118476d08a4f0280a154","item_id":"86273c707e:48","text":"无论作业完成时是否有错误都会运行的命令。"}
